## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1173-102">當控制項繫結至資料來源使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding>物件，您可以指定當資料來源的更新會使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataSourceUpdateMode>列舉型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1173-102">When a control is bound to a data source using a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> object, you can specify when an update to the data source will occur using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataSourceUpdateMode> enumeration.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1173-103">永遠不檢查更新模式時，您可以強制使用更新的資料來源<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.WriteValue%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1173-103">When the update mode is Never, you can force the data source to be updated by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.WriteValue%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="c1173-104">即使在更新模式設定為永不，當第一次建立繫結，因此一律會發生的最小的一項更新在將更新資料來源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1173-104">Even when the update mode is set to Never, the data source will be updated when the binding is first created, so at that least one update will always occur.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
